social_posts.post_text:
#invite My eyes I-GLUED to the table 👀 @vinegaryardldn and @greygoose currently have a wintery pop up where you can enjoy some cocktails alongside @nannybills and @badboypizzasoc a great spot to have a few with some pals!
#pizza #christmas

#Invite 🇪🇸 This meal was hard TAPAS up… 🤪 Delicious sharing plates at @maresco_soho, video footage transforming to photo edits, bit of a different style of editing for me, what do you think? (Shot on iPhone 13 Pro Max)

Highlights of the menu: 
Croquetas Menorquinas
Presa Iberica
Gigha Halibut with black rice

#tapas #londonfood #dinner

#Gifted There’s a SHIRO inside all of us! 🙌 Thrilled to have had the opportunity to try the lunch set menu at @shirosushilondon with a chefs selection of sashimi and sushi, rich yet light tonkotsu ramen among other tasty treats! Definitely recommend 👌 #JapaneseFood #Sushi #foodporn

#Gifted Which ‘wich is which? 🤔 🤷‍♂️ Popped down to @whichwichuk for lunch today and went for the Shrimp Po Boy and the Philly Cheesesteak. Can you guess which is which is wich is which is witch? It’s not as hard as it sounds 😜 #sandwich #sandwiches

🚨 #GIVEAWAY ALERT! 🚨 

@theathenianuk have just launched their “Eat Like A Greek” cookbook with 60 delicious recipes 😋 I’m giving away 1 copy of the book to a lucky winner, all you have to do is:

Follow @the.food.pundit
Follow @theathenianuk 
Tag 3 friends in the comments below (unlimited entries)

Winner will be selected on Sunday, good luck! 🤞 

#greekfood #competition #win
#Gifted Last weekend I HAGGIS Scotch Egg 👀 with a pork belly roast and all the trimmings at @thejuggedhare 🙌 #sundayroast #roast #scotchegg

#Gifted When dinner is more than OK 🥰 @okn1hoxton delivering the goods with a selection of international tapas dishes: top picks being the miso aubergine, croquettes and broccoli 🤤 #dinner #smallplates #tapas

#Gifted 🐔 Don’t FLAP over lunch 👀 @20ft_fried_chicken x @monkeyshoulder Have got you covered! The new chicken concept by @black_bear_burger at @markethallsoxfordstreet is only on menus until 8th July! Pick up a Beery Boulevard cocktail if you’re a negroni fan 💪 #wings #madeformixing #makeitmonkey

My Monday was BATTER than yours 🐠 Not really, it’s not a competition. It was a bloody good one though as I got to watch Djokovic play at the first day of @wimbledon as well as eat some fish and chips. 🙌 #fishandchips #Wimbledon

#Invite SCARAMOUCH SCARAMOUCH, WILL YOU DO THE DO FRANGO? 💃 Enjoying some piri-piri chicken, bacalhau cod fritters washed down with some sangria at @casadofrango_london on a Friday afternoon 👌 #portugesefood #piripiri #london #lunch

Yolk gotta be kidding me with the @burgerandbeyond #NationalBurgerDay special! 🍔 THE SESH-1 with a Dry Aged Beef Patty, American Cheese, Fried Egg, Szechwan & Garlic Mayo, Peng Yen Slaw and Crispy Chilli Oil. A definite must try, on the menu until the 31st August! 👍 #Gifted

#Invite Thank you Murray much 😊 The #NationalBurgerDay special fron @lucky_chip at @oldqueenshead running all of September: The Bill Murray - AGED BEEF PATTY, SOFT SHELL CRAB, GUACAMOLE, SPRING ONIONS, CHEESE, SPICY MAYO ANND GINGER SWEET CHILLI 👌
#Gifted 🇯🇵 Fried-Day lunch scenes 😍 Hot Chicken Sando from @japanesechickenshop at @vinegaryardldn alongside a signature chicken meal box 🥰 #friedchicken #karaage #sando
John Cena? I hardly know her. #dimsum #harcheungfun #johncena
LOKMA order in please! 👀 Just a little shoot I did for @lokma.bermondsey what do you think? #bottomlessbrunch #brunch

OH CAY! 👌 #Invite One of my favourite Vietnamese spots @caytrerestaurant invited me to try a breadth of their dishes, honestly so much to choose from as you can see 👀 Definitely order the Saigon Pho with extra fatty beef and delicious broth, the Vietnamese drip coffee with indulgent condensed milk and the claypot catfish for a burst of flavour with every bite! #vietnamese #vietnamesefood #pho #london

#invite CHICKA CHICKA YEAH! 🐔 @chicknsours x @drstingshothoney collab on the menu as of Wednesday 4th October! Be sure to head down and check them out, only on the menu for 2 weeks! #wings #chickenwings #fastfood #asianfood #fusionfood #london #londonfood #lunch #bottomless #londoneats

#Gifted 🇲🇽 Taco ‘bout a good dinner 🤪 So life’s been a bit mad, shout out to the @breddostacos gang who actually invited me down about a month ago to try the new Stoke Newington menu 👊 Highlights being the Baja Fish, Gringa de Carne Asada and the ceviche starter 👌 #taco #tacos #mexicanfood

#Gifted @coqfighteruk with an absolute Ala-BANGER! 🤠 🍔 ❤️ My favourite fried chicken joint in London has launched the limited time ALABAMA SLAMMER on the menu 🇺🇸 with fried chicken thigh, burnt jalapeño & spring onion butter, Alabama white BBQ sauce and shredded iceberg! Definitely one to try #Friedchicken #chickenburger #london
